thread.title: Women march for equal rights in London

title: Women march for equal rights in London
text:
Women march for equal rights in London 11:36am EST - 01:07 
Hundreds of people took to the streets of London on Sunday to say 'Time's Up' to issues including harassment and the gender pay gap. It comes as part of a series of marches taking place around the world over the weekend. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
